    <item>
      <title>瑞士银行在瑞士改革之前就增资 200 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ubs-is-adding-20-billion-in-capital-even-before-swiss-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂 (Sergio Ermotti) 表示，尽管瑞士政府计划从明年开始提高要求，但瑞银集团在整合瑞士信贷业务时，已经在其监管储备中增加了近 200 亿美元的资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ubs-is-adding-20-billion-in-capital-even-before-swiss-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 09:38:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国黄金购买热潮已连续第 18 个月延续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-s-gold-buying-spree-extends-to-18th-straight-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[4月份，中国央行连续第18个月扩大黄金储备，扩大购买热潮，推动贵金属创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-s-gold-buying-spree-extends-to-18th-straight-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 09:37:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
